{"pageProps":{"article":{"id":"39d4434d3c","title":"中央首长第五次接见内蒙四方面代表谈话纪要","origin":"","is_range_date":false,"dates":[{"id":"2c46870339","index":0,"year":1967,"month":4,"day":12,"articleId":"39d4434d3c"}],"tags":[{"id":"06af9ed14a","name":"肖华","type":"人物"},{"id":"0b2012c0b4","name":"革命三结合","type":"主题/事件"},{"id":"20ebde32a6","name":"王力","type":"人物"},{"id":"314ad57c4d","name":"对话","type":"文稿类型"},{"id":"3aaab89c2a","name":"刘少奇","type":"人物"},{"id":"40ffd466ef","name":"武斗","type":"主题/事件"},{"id":"4164db13ce","name":"内蒙古文革","type":"人物"},{"id":"523bb79e8f","name":"周恩来","type":"人物"},{"id":"57eea82497","name":"康生","type":"人物"},{"id":"5f4cf2fdf4","name":"青海文革","type":"人物"},{"id":"850a97e2ab","name":"李天佑","type":"人物"},{"id":"aa048f8141","name":"夺权","type":"主题/事件"},{"id":"aa9434abe4","name":"北京文革","type":"人物"},{"id":"ccf6dcdbbc","name":"吴涛","type":"人物"},{"id":"e46e45351b","name":"陈伯达","type":"人物"}],"aliases":[],"publications":[{"id":"GPCRv3","name":"中国文化大革命文库（第三版）","internal":true,"official":false,"type":"db","author":"宋永毅","files":""}],"authors":[{"id":"48606ca4e5","name":"陈伯达"},{"id":"7a99cebe4e","name":"周恩来"},{"id":"8bb7755376","name":"康生"}]},"publication_details":{"GPCRv3":{"comments":[],"contents":[{"id":"a6c0ac87ad","type":"title","text":"中央首长第五次接见内蒙四方面代表谈话纪要","index":0,"publicationId":"GPCRv3","articleId":"39d4434d3c"},{"id":"223c115864","type":"authors","text":"周恩来陈伯达康生","index":1,"publicationId":"GPCRv3","articleId":"39d4434d3c"},{"id":"478594d5b3","type":"appellation","text":"〖时间：一九六七年四月十二日二十三时五分至十二日一时四十五分。地点：人大会堂安徽厅。接见人：总理、伯达、康生、肖华、张春桥、王力、关锋、姚文元及总政，总参和各大军区负责人徐立清、李天佑、韩先楚、宋任穷、张国华、陈先瑞等。被接见人：区党委代表：高锦明、权星桓、康修民、李树德、李质、郭以清、张鲁。军区代表：吴涛、刘华香、肖应棠、黄厚、刘昌、王良太、姜文启、诸方玉、敖长锁和独立二师杨饱松、尤亚民、华民等。军区造反派代表：邵仲康等24人。呼三司等革命造反派代表：高树华、郝广德等57人。红卫军等保守组织代表：张三林等9人。王铎、王逸伦没让参加。〗","index":2,"publicationId":"GPCRv3","articleId":"39d4434d3c"},{"id":"9707405808","type":"paragraph","text":"总理：现在开会，内蒙古情况大致清楚了，已经两个多月了嘛！今天请后来的同志再谈谈。","index":3,"publicationId":"GPCRv3","articleId":"39d4434d3c"},{"id":"a49ce5362f","type":"paragraph","text":"郝广德：（给总理介绍）这是张孝同志。","index":4,"publicationId":"GPCRv3","articleId":"39d4434d3c"},{"id":"da92c9590d","type":"paragraph","text":"总理：那个学校的（翻材料）？","index":5,"publicationId":"GPCRv3","articleId":"39d4434d3c"},{"id":"e84ba03a80","type":"paragraph","text":"郝广德：“火车头”的。","index":6,"publicationId":"GPCRv3","articleId":"39d4434d3c"},{"id":"eb272087c3","type":"paragraph","text":"总理：有名字没有（指是否登记过）？","index":7,"publicationId":"GPCRv3","articleId":"39d4434d3c"},{"id":"d3f2979254","type":"paragraph","text":"赵刚，宋学孔：没有，今天才来的。","index":8,"publicationId":"GPCRv3","articleId":"39d4434d3c"},{"id":"1b94974f18","type":"paragraph","text":"总理：那一部分的？","index":9,"publicationId":"GPCRv3","articleId":"39d4434d3c"},{"id":"c6fb7b18c4","type":"paragraph","text":"郝广德：“火车头”的。（张孝说了一句，声音很低）","index":10,"publicationId":"GPCRv3","articleId":"39d4434d3c"},{"id":"e7158c9283","type":"paragraph","text":"总理：你能说话吗？火车头代表替他说说。","index":11,"publicationId":"GPCRv3","articleId":"39d4434d3c"},{"id":"2b03247578","type":"paragraph","text":"张孝：能！（旁边两人扶起）","index":12,"publicationId":"GPCRv3","articleId":"39d4434d3c"},{"id":"2cb83e4ec5","type":"paragraph","text":"总理，康生：坐下吧！坐下吧！","index":13,"publicationId":"GPCRv3","articleId":"39d4434d3c"},{"id":"315f656c92","type":"paragraph","text":"总理：不是还有一位火车头的同志嘛？","index":14,"publicationId":"GPCRv3","articleId":"39d4434d3c"},{"id":"9a05eaa499","type":"paragraph","text":"包长胜：有，我叫包长胜。","index":15,"publicationId":"GPCRv3","articleId":"39d4434d3c"},{"id":"629f0725ac","type":"paragraph","text":"总理：你替他谈一谈吧。（包讲张孝受迫害经过，谈到残废时）","index":16,"publicationId":"GPCRv3","articleId":"39d4434d3c"},{"id":"b412e7643d","type":"paragraph","text":"总理：治不好了吗？快送到北京医院！","index":17,"publicationId":"GPCRv3","articleId":"39d4434d3c"},{"id":"b4be56f819","type":"paragraph","text":"张孝：我说两句。","index":18,"publicationId":"GPCRv3","articleId":"39d4434d3c"},{"id":"70a738b484","type":"paragraph","text":"总理：坐着说吧！（总理抬起头）你谈吧！（对赵刚）快点送医院去看看。（张孝：控诉被迫害经过）","index":19,"publicationId":"GPCRv3","articleId":"39d4434d3c"},{"id":"309aab1e3b","type":"paragraph","text":"曹文生：他讲的与事实不符，他们写过反动标语。","index":20,"publicationId":"GPCRv3","articleId":"39d4434d3c"},{"id":"67f57232ae","type":"paragraph","text":"总理：什么标语？","index":21,"publicationId":"GPCRv3","articleId":"39d4434d3c"},{"id":"ae5650564e","type":"paragraph","text":"曹文生：“青松不怕火烧，‘火纵’不怕狗咬”，攻击解放军。","index":22,"publicationId":"GPCRv3","articleId":"39d4434d3c"},{"id":"c614279e70","type":"paragraph","text":"康生：就为这件事，应该不应该把人打成这个样子？","index":23,"publicationId":"GPCRv3","articleId":"39d4434d3c"},{"id":"7b32985867","type":"paragraph","text":"曹文生：谁打的，我不清楚。要严惩凶手，我们要为受害者申诉。（大家冷笑）","index":24,"publicationId":"GPCRv3","articleId":"39d4434d3c"},{"id":"ddbc94f97c","type":"paragraph","text":"（包长胜：严厉驳斥曹文生等人在资本主义反革命复辟逆流中破坏“抓革命，促生产”等罪恶活动。）","index":25,"publicationId":"GPCRv3","articleId":"39d4434d3c"},{"id":"c6ddc791cb","type":"paragraph","text":"总理：（对曹文生）我问你，现在为什么不放人？这是不是事实？！","index":26,"publicationId":"GPCRv3","articleId":"39d4434d3c"},{"id":"239faffc24","type":"paragraph","text":"曹文生：据说是放了。","index":27,"publicationId":"GPCRv3","articleId":"39d4434d3c"},{"id":"2bdd041dfa","type":"paragraph","text":"总理：就因为这条标语就抓人？","index":28,"publicationId":"GPCRv3","articleId":"39d4434d3c"},{"id":"0ca88e24ea","type":"paragraph","text":"曹文生：写的是反动标语。","index":29,"publicationId":"GPCRv3","articleId":"39d4434d3c"},{"id":"23575a9640","type":"paragraph","text":"总理：这样的标语，在北京都有，怎么能是反动标语呢？怎么能是攻击解放军呢？","index":30,"publicationId":"GPCRv3","articleId":"39d4434d3c"},{"id":"f8b0818a15","type":"paragraph","text":"康生：没有说解放军嘛！解放军你们说拥护，中央指示你们拥护不拥护？","index":31,"publicationId":"GPCRv3","articleId":"39d4434d3c"},{"id":"9bb5454b93","type":"paragraph","text":"曹文生：拥护！","index":32,"publicationId":"GPCRv3","articleId":"39d4434d3c"},{"id":"51a09c96ef","type":"paragraph","text":"康生：拥护为什么到现在还不放人？","index":33,"publicationId":"GPCRv3","articleId":"39d4434d3c"},{"id":"b56b8d7f59","type":"paragraph","text":"总理：拥护？！早就说了，你们到现在还不放人。","index":34,"publicationId":"GPCRv3","articleId":"39d4434d3c"},{"id":"6295a2b7f1","type":"paragraph","text":"高利陶（军区宣传部干事）：揭发张三林造谣惑众的事实。","index":35,"publicationId":"GPCRv3","articleId":"39d4434d3c"},{"id":"de6d4ce08e","type":"paragraph","text":"张三林：我不愿解释个人问题。（众笑）","index":36,"publicationId":"GPCRv3","articleId":"39d4434d3c"},{"id":"1fc302353a","type":"paragraph","text":"总理：你是不是三司的？","index":37,"publicationId":"GPCRv3","articleId":"39d4434d3c"},{"id":"f7dab9f442","type":"paragraph","text":"张三林：不是，我是红卫军的，橡胶厂的。","index":38,"publicationId":"GPCRv3","articleId":"39d4434d3c"},{"id":"a28f40932e","type":"paragraph","text":"总理：先说这件事，你回答这个问题：为什么还不放人？","index":39,"publicationId":"GPCRv3","articleId":"39d4434d3c"},{"id":"9a3ed22326","type":"paragraph","text":"曹文生：下午曾打过加急长途电话。他们制造停车事件，他们是不符合公安六条的。","index":40,"publicationId":"GPCRv3","articleId":"39d4434d3c"},{"id":"261259c249","type":"paragraph","text":"总理：那一条？你们扣了几个人？","index":41,"publicationId":"GPCRv3","articleId":"39d4434d3c"},{"id":"ebf6bc48aa","type":"paragraph","text":"曹文生：八、九个人。","index":42,"publicationId":"GPCRv3","articleId":"39d4434d3c"},{"id":"dfd717f53e","type":"paragraph","text":"总理：什么时候扣的？","index":43,"publicationId":"GPCRv3","articleId":"39d4434d3c"},{"id":"be51afdff7","type":"paragraph","text":"曹文生：二月五日扣了两个，五个是二月八日扣的。","index":44,"publicationId":"GPCRv3","articleId":"39d4434d3c"},{"id":"041f12f66b","type":"paragraph","text":"总理：二月八日到现在已有两个多月了，为什么到现在不放？","index":45,"publicationId":"GPCRv3","articleId":"39d4434d3c"},{"id":"0ad2ca957d","type":"paragraph","text":"康生：中央命令在你们那里算数不算数？","index":46,"publicationId":"GPCRv3","articleId":"39d4434d3c"},{"id":"d3654efe0c","type":"paragraph","text":"总理：四点指示有效没效？","index":47,"publicationId":"GPCRv3","articleId":"39d4434d3c"},{"id":"ff46a9cead","type":"paragraph","text":"张三林：有效，今天又打电话回去了。","index":48,"publicationId":"GPCRv3","articleId":"39d4434d3c"},{"id":"50ad55e898","type":"paragraph","text":"总理：有郊为什么还不放人？北京的同志来了没有？","index":49,"publicationId":"GPCRv3","articleId":"39d4434d3c"},{"id":"706885a41c","type":"paragraph","text":"李天佑：来了。（陈先瑞走到前面去）","index":50,"publicationId":"GPCRv3","articleId":"39d4434d3c"},{"id":"8deb5c4980","type":"paragraph","text":"总理：北京军区是一个小部队，军事接管呼和铁路局。（众：起立高呼：毛主席万岁！万岁！万万岁！）","index":51,"publicationId":"GPCRv3","articleId":"39d4434d3c"},{"id":"6f483523bb","type":"paragraph","text":"总理：你们为什么不放？就算有点嫌疑，已经扣了两个多月了嘛！","index":52,"publicationId":"GPCRv3","articleId":"39d4434d3c"},{"id":"b2968b12a4","type":"paragraph","text":"康生：抗拒两个多月了嘛！","index":53,"publicationId":"GPCRv3","articleId":"39d4434d3c"},{"id":"a3a5a9de02","type":"paragraph","text":"总理：（对曹）你还有什么辩护的？（曹文生没吭声的坐下了。）（包长胜继续揭发铁路局两条路线的斗争及曹破坏生产的罪行。）","index":54,"publicationId":"GPCRv3","articleId":"39d4434d3c"},{"id":"6c81a64f5d","type":"paragraph","text":"总理：铁路局问题知道了，现在由邮电局王连奎谈谈。王连奎揭×区控制邮电、非法偷听电话等罪行，谈了邮电局二月九日成立保守组织，十号就反夺权。这时总理、康生等首长都笑了）","index":55,"publicationId":"GPCRv3","articleId":"39d4434d3c"},{"id":"38d8b07433","type":"paragraph","text":"总理：你们有几派？","index":56,"publicationId":"GPCRv3","articleId":"39d4434d3c"},{"id":"514794d400","type":"paragraph","text":"王连奎：两派。","index":57,"publicationId":"GPCRv3","articleId":"39d4434d3c"},{"id":"0dc65b1c98","type":"paragraph","text":"总理：你们三司观点的有多少人？","index":58,"publicationId":"GPCRv3","articleId":"39d4434d3c"},{"id":"291dbdd457","type":"paragraph","text":"王连奎：我们三司观点的三百人，无产者一百多人。并说二月十号反夺权，他们叫“三结合”。","index":59,"publicationId":"GPCRv3","articleId":"39d4434d3c"},{"id":"6e9bc7c350","type":"paragraph","text":"总理：他们叫“三结合”？","index":60,"publicationId":"GPCRv3","articleId":"39d4434d3c"},{"id":"1b0cff1504","type":"paragraph","text":"王连奎：邮电局还调动农民保权！","index":61,"publicationId":"GPCRv3","articleId":"39d4434d3c"},{"id":"fa523f491c","type":"paragraph","text":"总理：保什么权？多少天？","index":62,"publicationId":"GPCRv3","articleId":"39d4434d3c"},{"id":"28a562de79","type":"paragraph","text":"王连奎：三天。","index":63,"publicationId":"GPCRv3","articleId":"39d4434d3c"},{"id":"208d0a3e79","type":"paragraph","text":"侯凤英：还搞录音。","index":64,"publicationId":"GPCRv3","articleId":"39d4434d3c"},{"id":"90da100a8d","type":"paragraph","text":"众：（他们对打电话都偷听，还延续时间。）（王连奎继续揭发盗用中央名义打电话等）","index":65,"publicationId":"GPCRv3","articleId":"39d4434d3c"},{"id":"2232cfaa2d","type":"paragraph","text":"总理：邮电局驻有多少军队？","index":66,"publicationId":"GPCRv3","articleId":"39d4434d3c"},{"id":"d7fa141100","type":"paragraph","text":"王连奎：一个加强连。","index":67,"publicationId":"GPCRv3","articleId":"39d4434d3c"},{"id":"b7f9edc32b","type":"paragraph","text":"总理：现在听听地方的。锡盟许名扬同志讲讲。","index":68,"publicationId":"GPCRv3","articleId":"39d4434d3c"},{"id":"cab8bbe075","type":"paragraph","text":"许名扬：现在还有十三人没放出来。","index":69,"publicationId":"GPCRv3","articleId":"39d4434d3c"},{"id":"5119a45061","type":"paragraph","text":"总理：你们那里还不放人？","index":70,"publicationId":"GPCRv3","articleId":"39d4434d3c"},{"id":"68b31c0662","type":"paragraph","text":"许名扬：不放。","index":71,"publicationId":"GPCRv3","articleId":"39d4434d3c"},{"id":"ce5bfd1ea1","type":"paragraph","text":"总理：什么时候问的？","index":72,"publicationId":"GPCRv3","articleId":"39d4434d3c"},{"id":"a8e7471b08","type":"paragraph","text":"许名扬：中午问的。","index":73,"publicationId":"GPCRv3","articleId":"39d4434d3c"},{"id":"184dab073f","type":"paragraph","text":"总理：吴涛同志，这个事情交给你解决。","index":74,"publicationId":"GPCRv3","articleId":"39d4434d3c"},{"id":"79429f7d3c","type":"paragraph","text":"（吴涛：马上打电话）","index":75,"publicationId":"GPCRv3","articleId":"39d4434d3c"},{"id":"1624d96339","type":"paragraph","text":"（乌盟玉宝讲扣押人的情况，哲盟郭玉讲一人“畏罪自杀”问题。黄宝玉补充哲盟农村资本主义复辟情况。）","index":76,"publicationId":"GPCRv3","articleId":"39d4434d3c"},{"id":"940c4ba24b","type":"paragraph","text":"陈振中（巴盟代表）：听说部队支持煤矿夺权后，现在停掌子面。现在三十多人未放，他们说是中央军委指示的。","index":77,"publicationId":"GPCRv3","articleId":"39d4434d3c"},{"id":"022542b334","type":"paragraph","text":"肖华、王力：这是造谣！","index":78,"publicationId":"GPCRv3","articleId":"39d4434d3c"},{"id":"6852cf3944","type":"paragraph","text":"总理：（叫起兰州司令员说）你们处理。（又对吴涛同志）注意，我们还要和你们单独谈谈。（又问了内蒙日报社情况。）","index":79,"publicationId":"GPCRv3","articleId":"39d4434d3c"},{"id":"f6239a4904","type":"paragraph","text":"李雨楼：报社压制得很厉害，现在军队和红卫军非法占据报社。","index":80,"publicationId":"GPCRv3","articleId":"39d4434d3c"},{"id":"7f287d65e3","type":"paragraph","text":"总理：报社几派？","index":81,"publicationId":"GPCRv3","articleId":"39d4434d3c"},{"id":"412e4d33e8","type":"paragraph","text":"王力：报社有保守派吗？","index":82,"publicationId":"GPCRv3","articleId":"39d4434d3c"},{"id":"fe59792b10","type":"paragraph","text":"李雨楼：两派。他们还有一百多人。","index":83,"publicationId":"GPCRv3","articleId":"39d4434d3c"},{"id":"2877d97a1d","type":"paragraph","text":"总理：报社谁管？","index":84,"publicationId":"GPCRv3","articleId":"39d4434d3c"},{"id":"9e41b5593e","type":"paragraph","text":"李雨楼：他们掌权着呢！","index":85,"publicationId":"GPCRv3","articleId":"39d4434d3c"},{"id":"f6e123f04c","type":"paragraph","text":"总理：登什么内容？","index":86,"publicationId":"GPCRv3","articleId":"39d4434d3c"},{"id":"70c96f2824","type":"paragraph","text":"李雨楼：没听总理指示，登了地方问题。","index":87,"publicationId":"GPCRv3","articleId":"39d4434d3c"},{"id":"68dbeb5817","type":"paragraph","text":"众：登“抗大”，登军区。","index":88,"publicationId":"GPCRv3","articleId":"39d4434d3c"},{"id":"a421a4b010","type":"paragraph","text":"总理：有报纸吗？","index":89,"publicationId":"GPCRv3","articleId":"39d4434d3c"},{"id":"5a2302e089","type":"paragraph","text":"李雨楼：没有带，我是从监狱出来直接上火车的。（黄宝玉、高树华等送上两份报纸。）","index":90,"publicationId":"GPCRv3","articleId":"39d4434d3c"},{"id":"94df48fdc8","type":"paragraph","text":"总理：高树华同志谈谈“联动”情况。","index":91,"publicationId":"GPCRv3","articleId":"39d4434d3c"},{"id":"62796db810","type":"paragraph","text":"（高树华谈了中学生中“联动”分子问题。）","index":92,"publicationId":"GPCRv3","articleId":"39d4434d3c"},{"id":"7236eb9692","type":"paragraph","text":"总理：让二中讲讲。（二中代表任卫东讲了“联动”罪恶的枪的问题。）","index":93,"publicationId":"GPCRv3","articleId":"39d4434d3c"},{"id":"071b8476f6","type":"paragraph","text":"高树华：他们还有电台。","index":94,"publicationId":"GPCRv3","articleId":"39d4434d3c"},{"id":"8abc1f306d","type":"paragraph","text":"总理：还有电台？有名单吗？给我，有多少人？","index":95,"publicationId":"GPCRv3","articleId":"39d4434d3c"},{"id":"14a88aff07","type":"paragraph","text":"任卫东：十几个。","index":96,"publicationId":"GPCRv3","articleId":"39d4434d3c"},{"id":"c5b16fdef6","type":"paragraph","text":"高树华：还有反动标语：“打倒康生”等。","index":97,"publicationId":"GPCRv3","articleId":"39d4434d3c"},{"id":"40c1e81795","type":"paragraph","text":"梁音亭（军区后勤部）：他们游行时打着刘少奇的象。","index":98,"publicationId":"GPCRv3","articleId":"39d4434d3c"},{"id":"f7d41f5b61","type":"paragraph","text":"黄宝玉：新华书店一千多张刘少奇的象都被他们拿出来了。","index":99,"publicationId":"GPCRv3","articleId":"39d4434d3c"},{"id":"240d124c41","type":"paragraph","text":"众：还举起象高呼口号。","index":100,"publicationId":"GPCRv3","articleId":"39d4434d3c"},{"id":"4d710a65bf","type":"paragraph","text":"张三林：我们从新华书店拿出来烧的。","index":101,"publicationId":"GPCRv3","articleId":"39d4434d3c"},{"id":"a4386cd184","type":"paragraph","text":"康生：你们拿着刘少奇的象游行没有？有没有四个象？","index":102,"publicationId":"GPCRv3","articleId":"39d4434d3c"},{"id":"8fa43d743c","type":"paragraph","text":"张三林：不知道。（霍道余揭露他们批判刘少奇是假的）","index":103,"publicationId":"GPCRv3","articleId":"39d4434d3c"},{"id":"2eb14997af","type":"paragraph","text":"高惠娟：二中赵玉花说，苏修、蒙修支持三司，周总理也支持三司。","index":104,"publicationId":"GPCRv3","articleId":"39d4434d3c"},{"id":"66cffa37f9","type":"paragraph","text":"总理：捏造！","index":105,"publicationId":"GPCRv3","articleId":"39d4434d3c"},{"id":"3cac7dcf26","type":"paragraph","text":"韩文达：他们在火车上审问时说：王力是个大混蛋，是三司的后台，要挖王力的根子。（总理、王力等大笑）","index":106,"publicationId":"GPCRv3","articleId":"39d4434d3c"},{"id":"429b9bf923","type":"paragraph","text":"曹燕玲（军区红色造反团）：军区文办正在整理王力同志的材料。","index":107,"publicationId":"GPCRv3","articleId":"39d4434d3c"},{"id":"79a47baa8b","type":"paragraph","text":"包力陶：怀疑中央的根子，这是军区某些人，他们要挖王力同志的根子。","index":108,"publicationId":"GPCRv3","articleId":"39d4434d3c"},{"id":"31cd5d536a","type":"paragraph","text":"总理：王逸伦的报告是不是都听了？","index":109,"publicationId":"GPCRv3","articleId":"39d4434d3c"},{"id":"021e3a3522","type":"paragraph","text":"众：听了。有的是三月三十一日，有的在四月七日。","index":110,"publicationId":"GPCRv3","articleId":"39d4434d3c"},{"id":"9f350ee3df","type":"paragraph","text":"包力陶：（详细揭露×区问题）他们说造反派在“一·二二”、“一·二五”事件上是 吃里爬 外。（众站起来指王良太：说过没有？）","index":111,"publicationId":"GPCRv3","articleId":"39d4434d3c"},{"id":"95345c027d","type":"paragraph","text":"王良太：说过。","index":112,"publicationId":"GPCRv3","articleId":"39d4434d3c"},{"id":"1bc38867d1","type":"paragraph","text":"（包力陶揭露军区某些领导人造谣蒙蔽群众，刘昌传达反革命策略问题。）","index":113,"publicationId":"GPCRv3","articleId":"39d4434d3c"},{"id":"be75d3a82b","type":"paragraph","text":"康小春：德山（呼市军分区付参谋长）曾念过一个特好消息说：“中央叫各大军区学内蒙。”","index":114,"publicationId":"GPCRv3","articleId":"39d4434d3c"},{"id":"f88ea2c8cb","type":"paragraph","text":"总理：（手挥一份传单）我这里也有一份，纯属造谣。","index":115,"publicationId":"GPCRv3","articleId":"39d4434d3c"},{"id":"f346cb5203","type":"paragraph","text":"陈永华：今天六点半来电话说：××二师协助保守派对工学院等革命造反派实行武斗。","index":116,"publicationId":"GPCRv3","articleId":"39d4434d3c"},{"id":"1847ec24b9","type":"paragraph","text":"张鸿喜：我也揭×师情况。……","index":117,"publicationId":"GPCRv3","articleId":"39d4434d3c"},{"id":"854e4aa428","type":"paragraph","text":"总理：王志有谈谈。","index":118,"publicationId":"GPCRv3","articleId":"39d4434d3c"},{"id":"91dcc14892","type":"paragraph","text":"王志有（八一八）：他们说有两条黑线，一个黑根，要揪李富春、李雪峰、要揪黑根！（回头质问王良太）你说黑根是谁？","index":119,"publicationId":"GPCRv3","articleId":"39d4434d3c"},{"id":"7c9295ff36","type":"paragraph","text":"众：（质问）王良太站起来！（总理没让王讲。）","index":120,"publicationId":"GPCRv3","articleId":"39d4434d3c"},{"id":"3f165ec987","type":"paragraph","text":"总理：不要问了，很显然黑根就是中央嘛！","index":121,"publicationId":"GPCRv3","articleId":"39d4434d3c"},{"id":"d479eefa1b","type":"paragraph","text":"王志有：河西公司反夺权后，报喜时，我们提出意见，说不要让外边的人到厂子里来。他们说是总理点头，林彪同志也在场。","index":122,"publicationId":"GPCRv3","articleId":"39d4434d3c"},{"id":"40485d3876","type":"paragraph","text":"总理：真是！造这种谣言。（蔚洋：揭露电台军代表造谣和反夺权问题。）","index":123,"publicationId":"GPCRv3","articleId":"39d4434d3c"},{"id":"23431df2a7","type":"paragraph","text":"总理：全部是造谣。","index":124,"publicationId":"GPCRv3","articleId":"39d4434d3c"},{"id":"46785e118a","type":"paragraph","text":"王力：造谣。","index":125,"publicationId":"GPCRv3","articleId":"39d4434d3c"},{"id":"84071d62b4","type":"paragraph","text":"蔚洋：他们说，林副主席说：“你们打的不狠，手太软！不如青海，进度不快。”","index":126,"publicationId":"GPCRv3","articleId":"39d4434d3c"},{"id":"7a842894e4","type":"paragraph","text":"总理：青海文件你们看到没有？","index":127,"publicationId":"GPCRv3","articleId":"39d4434d3c"},{"id":"048754340c","type":"paragraph","text":"众：没有。","index":128,"publicationId":"GPCRv3","articleId":"39d4434d3c"},{"id":"c1f8ac2451","type":"paragraph","text":"总理：（对于顺昌）你们记者有文件，明天给读一读。","index":129,"publicationId":"GPCRv3","articleId":"39d4434d3c"},{"id":"d38996c10d","type":"paragraph","text":"蔚洋：他们造谣说：李天佑根本不支持三司。","index":130,"publicationId":"GPCRv3","articleId":"39d4434d3c"},{"id":"f1c36ba1d8","type":"paragraph","text":"李天佑：我白天去东纵，晚上又从东纵东门到楼上，他们纯属是造谣。","index":131,"publicationId":"GPCRv3","articleId":"39d4434d3c"},{"id":"2b609084df","type":"paragraph","text":"总理：电台有多少军队？","index":132,"publicationId":"GPCRv3","articleId":"39d4434d3c"},{"id":"ed4ea92e02","type":"paragraph","text":"蔚洋：由一个班增至一个排。","index":133,"publicationId":"GPCRv3","articleId":"39d4434d3c"},{"id":"b6f3923cf3","type":"paragraph","text":"总理：周文孝把农村发枪情况谈谈。","index":134,"publicationId":"GPCRv3","articleId":"39d4434d3c"},{"id":"698315c5fd","type":"paragraph","text":"周文孝：给桃花公社发17枝枪，30发子弹。","index":135,"publicationId":"GPCRv3","articleId":"39d4434d3c"},{"id":"bd5434fc49","type":"paragraph","text":"总理：今天会到此结束了。明天九点钟再开一次，内蒙问题就结束了。让肖华同志与军区同志谈一谈，还有记者和联络员同志同大家谈一谈，还有什么材料送上来，明天开会时间九点。不要再增加了，观点不要说了，已经很清楚了，已经两个多月了嘛！不然人越来越多。群众不要互相对立，不要着急。你们是按毛泽东思想办事的，要等待一下。内蒙古自治区地区大，分区多，还有各旗县，还有牧区，电话传达不到的可以派人嘛！","index":136,"publicationId":"GPCRv3","articleId":"39d4434d3c"},{"id":"cd3f5d178b","type":"paragraph","text":"铁路局去的部队明天天亮就到了。铁路那位同志，明天送到医院，总是可以治好的。","index":137,"publicationId":"GPCRv3","articleId":"39d4434d3c"},{"id":"2765494ff3","type":"paragraph","text":"明天晚上九点开会，有材料还可以送上来。要等待中央的布置。同志们受苦了，这是为革命嘛！我们一定要把边疆的问题解决好。明天结束这个会，要靠革命造反派团结起来。散会。","index":138,"publicationId":"GPCRv3","articleId":"39d4434d3c"},{"id":"591c5ecd5a","type":"paragraph","text":"（全体起立，鼓掌欢送总理及各位首长，总理等招手致意，大家呼口号：毛主席万岁！万岁！万万岁！）","index":139,"publicationId":"GPCRv3","articleId":"39d4434d3c"}],"page":{"id":"e988b92f07","publicationId":"GPCRv3","articleId":"39d4434d3c","start":0,"end":0}}}},"__N_SSG":true}